<heading id="5A24A609FFB13969EBD2C3C9FEA35E22" bold="true" box="[227,348,1274,1300]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" reason="3">
<emphasis id="33A7CD77FFB13969EBD2C3C9FEA35E22" bold="true" box="[227,348,1274,1300]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="016C1165FFB13969EBD2C218FC6E5E5C" blockId="31.[226,1437,1323,1386]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">OL/OH = 1.38–1.42. Otoliths oval, moderately thick, higher in the middle. Sulcus wide, not divided into ostium and cauda, with an oblong colliculum in the center.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
